Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Naturalist To implement a naturalist AI, extend this class and implement method run.
Node An instance represents a single square cell on the map.
RandomWalkNaturalist An instance contains method run() for a player that does a random walk of the island.
Ship An instance is the terrain type for a ship, the home base for an explorer, where the explorer starts.
Simulator Main class for the naturalist simulator.
 

Exception Summary
CapacityExceededException Thrown when Naturalist.collect is called but the naturalist is already carrying the maximum number of animals.
IllegalMoveException Thrown if the naturalist attempts to move between two non-adjacent nodes
SpecimenNotFoundException Thrown if Naturalist.collect is called for an animal that isn't present
TriumphException Naturalist.moveTo throws this exception when all animals have been brought to the ship.
